The rule in Eq. (1) shows that the position of the leader is updated only based on the food source. The parameters c2 and c3 are random real numbers that are uniformly generated in the region of [0,1]. The most critical parameter c1 used to keep the poise between exploration and exploitation drifts in SSA is calculated as follows:2c1=2×e-4×lL2,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
